ISLAMABAD, Nov 03 (APP):Federal Minister for Information, Broadcasting, National Heritage and Culture on Sunday expressed deep grief over demise of the wife of senior journalist Altaf Hussain Qureshi.
The minister, in a condolence message, prayed to the Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the irreparable loss with fortitude.
